'''帕里克-德林氧化反应'''（Parikh-Doering oxidation）以[[二甲亚砜|二甲亚砜]]为[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]，[[三氧化硫吡啶|三氧化硫-吡啶络合物]]为活化剂，[[三乙胺|三乙胺]]为碱而将[[伯醇|伯醇]]和[[仲醇|仲醇]]转化为相应的[[醛|醛]][[酮|酮]]。

[[Image:Parikh-Doering_reaction.svg|center]]

反应在近环境温度（一般为0℃）下进行时，可以只产生少量的甲硫甲基醚副产物。<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Sulfur Trioxide in the Oxidation of Alcohols by Dimethyl Sulfoxide
| author = J. R. Parikh and W. v. E. Doering | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society | year = 1967 | volume = 89 | pages = 5505-5507 | doi = 10.1021/ja00997a067}}</ref>

==反应机理==
二甲亚砜与三氧化硫在0℃或室温下发生加成，并受到醇进攻，生成关键的[[烷氧基|烷氧基]][[锍|锍]]离子中间体(6)。

[[Image:Mechanism_of_the_Parikh-Doering_Oxidation_-_Part_1.png|center]]

该中间体接下来被碱[[去质子化|去质子化]]为相应的[[硫叶立德|硫叶立德]]，然后硫叶立德经五元环过渡态、分解放出[[二甲硫醚|二甲硫醚]]，得到醛酮。

[[Image:Parikh-Doering_Oxidation_Mechanism_Part2_2nd_edition.png|center]]

==应用==
埃文斯等在合成(–)-kumausallene 时就用到了帕里克-德林氧化反应。（注意所用的典型反应条件）<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Enantioselective Total Synthesis of the Nonisoprenoid Sesquiterpene (-)-Kumausallene | author = P. A. Evans, V. S. Murthy, J. D. Roseman, A. L. Rheingold | journal = Angewandte Chemie International Edition| year = 1999 | volume = 38 | pages = 3175-3177 | doi = 10.1002/(SICI)1521-3773(19991102)38:21<3175::AID-ANIE3175>3.0.CO;2-M}}</ref>

[[Image:parikh-doeringexample.png|center]]

尼科拉乌的cortistatin全合成中也使用了该反应。<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Total Synthesis and Biological Evaluation of Cortistatins A and J and Analogues Thereof | author = K. C. Nicolaou, Xiao-Shui Peng, Ya-Ping Sun, Damien Polet, Bin Zou, Chek Shik Lim, and David Y.-K. Chen | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society | year = 2009 | volume = 131 | pages = 10587–10597 | doi = 10.1021/ja902939t}}</ref> 

